data.description: This spacious home and yard is ready for you.  4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, and one BIG backyard!  Imagine the possibilities in the back!  Pool, play set, storage building, batting cage, BBQ, entertaining,. All can be done, while partaking on this expansive back porch. Enjoy the outdoors, with no one behind you. Inside is a well laid out house plan.  A flex room that could be an office or that 4th bedroom. Kitchen, dining, and breakfast bar. Living room with beautiful plantation shutters. Formal dining and full bath round out the downstairs. Upstairs has so much to offer.  A Dedicated work space at the top of the stair well. An awesome Living/flex room that would be great for gaming, toys, sleepovers, etc. Two large guest bedrooms with full bath and one grand primary suite. Primary has built in shelving, sitting area, and a glorious space for that king size bed.  En suite includes 2 walk in closets, soaking tub, separate shower and double vanity. Wow, Enough said!! Come see today!
